ing statuses without raising error (success, completed, or stopped)                                           &#xA;BEGIN              &#xA;    &#xA; SET @KeepWaiting = 0                          &#xA; SET @DidPackageFail = 0     &#xA;                                  &#xA;END&#xA;&#xA;END&#xA;&#xA;SELECT @DidPackageFail"
